snippet.title: Comics, superheroes and the Intellectual Dark Web, Jordan Greenhall & Akira the Don
snippet.description:
Akira the Don created a new genre of music, Meaningwave, combining the words of high profile intellectual dark web intellectuals such as Jordan Peterson and Joe Rogan with lo-fi music. Jordan Greenhall is a celebrated futurist and thinker.

Both are huge fans of comic book culture. In this film they discuss the similarities between the Intellectual Dark Web and the superhero archetype.

Also see: Genuine Conversation and the Intellectual Dark Web, Jordan Greenhall - https://youtu.be/tQGksc1I7rA

And: The Meaningwave Universe, with Akira the Don - https://youtu.be/UYUEBGtDdvY
